Other:The SE Custom 24 brings the original PRS design platform to the high-quality, more affordable SE line up of instruments. Its versatile sounds come from the SE 85/5 Treble and Bass pickups, which have volume and push-pull tone controls and a 3-way pickup selector. The SE Custom 24 is a modern classic with roadworthy durability, addictive playability, and wide array of tones, making it a perfect workhorse guitar. Includes gig bag.
